---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Arte Multisensorial — Sibila">
<div class="page-hero sub-hero-img fade-up">
  <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">Sibila · Mundo 02</div>
  <h1><span data-lang="es">Cuando el arte<br><em>se respira.</em></span><span data-lang="en" style="display:none">When art<br><em>is breathed.</em></span></h1>
  <p class="page-hero-sub" data-lang="es">Instalaciones olfativas que transforman conciertos, exposiciones y performances en experiencias inmersivas y memorables.</p>
  <p class="page-hero-sub" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Olfactory installations that transform concerts, exhibitions and performances into immersive, memorable experiences.</p>
</div>

<section class="arte-projects">
  <div class="section-label fade-up" data-es="Proyectos realizados" data-en="Completed projects">Proyectos realizados</div>
  <div class="arte-proj-list">
    <div class="arte-proj-item fade-up">
      <div class="arte-proj-num">01</div>
      <div>
        <div class="arte-proj-cat">Festival · Jerez de la Frontera</div>
        <div class="arte-proj-title" data-lang="es">Festival de Flamenco en Jerez</div>
        <div class="arte-proj-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Flamenco Festival in Jerez</div>
        <p class="arte-proj-text" data-lang="es">Creación de una atmósfera olfativa para el escenario principal: tierra mojada, azahar y tabaco negro evocando el alma del sur. El público recibió tarjetas olfativas sincronizadas con la actuación.</p>
        <p class="arte-proj-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Creation of an olfactory atmosphere for the main stage: wet earth, orange blossom and black tobacco evoking the soul of the south. The audience received scent cards synchronized with the performance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="arte-proj-item fade-up">
      <div class="arte-proj-num">02</div>
      <div>
        <div class="arte-proj-cat">Concierto · Barcelona</div>
        <div class="arte-proj-title">Marco Mezquida</div>
        <p class="arte-proj-text" data-lang="es">Composición aromática sincronizada con la evolución del concierto: notas frescas en la improvisación, profundidad de maderas en los momentos contemplativos. Una sinfonía que se respira.</p>
        <p class="arte-proj-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Aromatic composition synchronized with the concert's evolution: fresh notes during improvisation, deep wood notes during contemplative moments. A symphony you breathe.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="arte-proj-item fade-up">
      <div class="arte-proj-num">03</div>
      <div>
        <div class="arte-proj-cat" data-lang="es">Moda · París</div>
        <div class="arte-proj-cat" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Fashion · Paris</div>
        <div class="arte-proj-title" data-lang="es">Pasarela en París</div>
        <div class="arte-proj-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Runway in Paris</div>
        <p class="arte-proj-text" data-lang="es">Cada prenda acompañada de su propia narrativa olfativa, fusionando moda y perfumería en una experiencia bidimensional: vista y olfato.</p>
        <p class="arte-proj-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Each garment accompanied by its own olfactory narrative, fusing fashion and perfumery into a two-dimensional experience: sight and smell.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="arte-how">
  <div class="section-label light fade-up" data-es="Cómo trabajo" data-en="How I work">Cómo trabajo</div>
  <div class="arte-how-grid">
    <div class="arte-how-step fade-up">
      <div class="arte-how-title" data-lang="es">Idea</div>
      <div class="arte-how-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Idea</div>
      <p class="arte-how-text" data-lang="es">Conversamos sobre tu visión artística, el mensaje y las emociones que buscas evocar.</p>
      <p class="arte-how-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">We talk about your artistic vision, the message and the emotions you want to evoke.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="arte-how-step fade-up">
      <div class="arte-how-title" data-lang="es">Concepto olfativo</div>
      <div class="arte-how-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Olfactory concept</div>
      <p class="arte-how-text" data-lang="es">Traduzco tu lenguaje creativo en una paleta aromática coherente con tu obra.</p>
      <p class="arte-how-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">I translate your creative language into an aromatic palette coherent with your work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="arte-how-step fade-up">
      <div class="arte-how-title" data-lang="es">Instalación</div>
      <div class="arte-how-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Installation</div>
      <p class="arte-how-text" data-lang="es">Integramos el componente olfativo en tu espacio, creando una atmósfera inmersiva.</p>
      <p class="arte-how-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">We integrate the olfactory component into your space, creating an immersive atmosphere.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="sub-cta fade-up">
  <h2><span data-lang="es">¿Tienes un proyecto artístico?<br><em>Hablemos.</em></span><span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Have an artistic project?<br><em>Let's talk.</em></span></h2>
  <p data-lang="es">El aroma puede amplificar tu obra de formas que la vista y el sonido no alcanzan.</p>
  <p data-lang="en" style="display:none">Scent can amplify your work in ways that sight and sound cannot.</p>
  <div class="sub-cta-btns">
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary"><span data-es="Colabora conmigo" data-en="Collaborate with me">Colabora conmigo</span></a>
    <a href="https://wa.me/34608543705" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank">💬 WhatsApp</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Layout>

<style>
.sub-hero-img{background-image:url('/images/botanica-herbs.png');}
.arte-projects{padding:90px 80px;background:var(--cream);}
.arte-proj-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin-top:48px;}
.arte-proj-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;gap:48px;padding:44px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(200,134,42,.12);align-items:center;}
.arte-proj-num{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:4rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(200,134,42,.12);}
.arte-proj-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:10px;}
.arte-proj-cat{font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:10px;}
.arte-proj-text{font-size:.86rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text-muted);}
.arte-how{padding:90px 80px;background:var(--dark);}
.arte-how-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;margin-top:48px;}
.arte-how-step{padding:44px 36px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);}
.arte-how-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.4rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--cream);margin-bottom:12px;}
.arte-how-text{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.9;color:rgba(245,240,232,.42);}
.sub-cta{padding:90px 80px;background:var(--cream);text-align:center;}
.sub-cta h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3.5rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:20px;}
.sub-cta h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--amber);}
.sub-cta p{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.9;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto 36px;}
.sub-cta-btns{display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
@media(max-width:768px){
  .arte-projects,.arte-how,.sub-cta{padding:60px 20px;}
  .arte-proj-item{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .arte-how-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
</style>